01:34:14.719 --> 01:34:18.149
grateful. We're so thankful for all that

01:34:18.159 --> 01:34:21.030
you've done and all that you continue to

01:34:21.040 --> 01:34:22.550
do.

01:34:22.560 --> 01:34:27.430
We magnify you. We glorify you. We thank

01:34:27.440 --> 01:34:30.070
you, Father.

01:34:30.080 --> 01:34:31.910
Now, that's interesting. See, when you

01:34:31.920 --> 01:34:33.750
guys started doing that, I saw a vision

01:34:33.760 --> 01:34:36.470
and I saw an eagle.

01:34:36.480 --> 01:34:40.709
It's the eagle that flies high.

01:34:40.719 --> 01:34:42.629
You see, it had a... you know,

01:34:42.639 --> 01:34:44.229
whenever you see the eagle and its

01:34:44.229 --> 01:34:44.239
back

01:34:44.239 --> 01:34:46.470
goes like this, but this time he

01:34:46.480 --> 01:34:50.310
had his wings and he was pushing up.

01:34:50.320 --> 01:34:52.709
It's the worship

01:34:52.719 --> 01:34:56.310
teachable moments.

01:34:56.320 --> 01:34:58.390
I think, like I said, I think the Lord...

01:34:58.400 --> 01:34:59.750
because I asked him and said, 'What is it

01:34:59.760 --> 01:35:03.430
about today?'He said, 'Humble

01:35:03.430 --> 01:35:03.440
yourself.'This

01:35:03.440 --> 01:35:05.350
is it. Stripping off all the stuff

01:35:05.360 --> 01:35:06.950
and all the stuff going on there. Teach

01:35:06.960 --> 01:35:08.709
people.

01:35:08.719 --> 01:35:12.070
Again, another lesson. Teach people.

01:35:12.080 --> 01:35:17.669
This strips you

01:35:17.679 --> 01:35:20.629
because that's where he's at.

01:35:20.639 --> 01:35:23.750
We talk about where we are. Humble

01:35:23.760 --> 01:35:26.390
yourself. Humble yourself underneath the

01:35:26.400 --> 01:35:31.030
mighty hand of God.

01:35:31.040 --> 01:35:37.830
Finding songs to sing.

01:35:37.840 --> 01:35:43.350
My favorites are just Kim Clement.

01:35:43.360 --> 01:35:47.110
I was looking for it.

01:35:47.120 --> 01:35:49.030
I listen to it over and over again. This

01:35:49.040 --> 01:35:50.629
is usually what takes me right into the

01:35:50.639 --> 01:36:00.790
river.

01:36:00.800 --> 01:36:06.229
Hold that one note to everybody

01:36:06.239 --> 01:36:13.750
all over the world. Sing that one note.

01:36:13.760 --> 01:36:24.390
Beautiful.

01:36:24.400 --> 01:36:26.390
This is what I talk about when I say

01:36:26.400 --> 01:36:29.110
you find the vein.

01:36:29.120 --> 01:36:32.070
This is what I do. You have to

01:36:32.080 --> 01:36:33.750
find the vein. It's like finding

01:36:33.760 --> 01:36:36.070
it when they draw your blood. It's like

01:36:36.080 --> 01:36:38.550
