01:36:38.560 --> 01:36:40.950
When you hit it and you go

01:36:40.960 --> 01:36:43.350
down that river, this is when it carries

01:36:43.360 --> 01:36:45.990
you. But you've got to find it first. You

01:36:46.000 --> 01:36:48.950
don't just jump in it.

01:36:48.960 --> 01:36:50.790
A lot of times what you see on this

01:36:50.800 --> 01:36:53.189
is he's already waiting.

01:36:53.199 --> 01:36:59.590
This is what I do in my own time

01:36:59.600 --> 01:37:02.470
and listen to Kim. This is how I do

01:37:02.480 --> 01:37:04.550
it. Now, most of you maybe are veterans

01:37:04.560 --> 01:37:05.669
and you're saying, 'Well, Brandon,

01:37:05.679 --> 01:37:07.270
you're doing it wrong.'But this is how

01:37:07.280 --> 01:37:08.310
I do it.

01:37:08.320 --> 01:37:11.750
And there's a lot of babies on here.

01:37:11.760 --> 01:37:18.310
You find it. You worship.

01:37:21.600 --> 01:37:25.430
Soul of my soul,

01:37:25.440 --> 01:37:28.629
life of my life.

01:37:28.639 --> 01:37:41.430
Worship the Lord.

01:37:41.440 --> 01:37:47.030
Beautiful.

01:37:47.040 --> 01:37:50.149
Do you want to go

01:37:50.159 --> 01:37:53.669
to the mountain?

01:37:53.679 --> 01:37:55.590
We shake it off.

01:37:55.600 --> 01:37:58.709
Do you want to go

01:37:58.719 --> 01:38:03.910
to the mountain of the Lord?

01:38:03.920 --> 01:38:07.030
There is a place

01:38:07.040 --> 01:38:10.550
