01:38:10.560 --> 01:38:18.709
in

01:38:18.719 --> 01:38:23.109
the mountain of the

01:38:23.119 --> 01:38:25.430
Lord.

01:38:25.440 --> 01:38:28.310
Do you want to go

01:38:28.320 --> 01:38:32.709
to the mountain of the Lord?

01:38:32.719 --> 01:38:35.750
There is a place

01:38:35.760 --> 01:38:39.270
for those who are lonely

01:38:39.280 --> 01:38:43.590
in the mountain of the Lord.

01:38:43.600 --> 01:38:45.189
Everybody watching, no matter what

01:38:45.199 --> 01:38:48.229
nation you're at, you're welcome.

01:38:48.239 --> 01:38:51.270
We have come to Zion, the city of the

01:38:51.280 --> 01:38:54.790
living God, the heavenly Jerusalem.

01:38:54.800 --> 01:38:58.070
We have come

01:38:58.080 --> 01:39:00.870
to God, the judge of all. The spirits

01:39:00.880 --> 01:39:03.350
have just been made perfect. We have

01:39:03.360 --> 01:39:05.109
come to an innumerable company of

01:39:05.119 --> 01:39:07.510
angels.

01:39:07.520 --> 01:39:09.189
We have come to the general assembly in

01:39:09.199 --> 01:39:11.350
the church of the firstborn whose names

01:39:11.360 --> 01:39:13.910
are in heaven. We have come to Jesus the

01:39:13.920 --> 01:39:15.910
mediator of the new covenant and to the

01:39:15.920 --> 01:39:17.990
blood of sprinkling that speaks of

01:39:18.000 --> 01:39:19.750
better things than that of Abel. Come

01:39:19.760 --> 01:39:22.709
on, let's lift our hands. Glorify the

01:39:22.719 --> 01:39:34.390
Lord.

01:39:37.199 --> 01:39:44.390
I can hear your voice.

01:39:44.400 --> 01:39:48.070
I can touch your face.

01:39:48.080 --> 01:39:52.470
There is a place

01:39:52.480 --> 01:39:54.550
of mercy

01:39:54.560 --> 01:40:02.310
in the mountain of the Lord.

01:40:09.520 --> 01:40:13.109
Your

01:40:13.119 --> 01:40:16.870
presence,

01:40:16.880 --> 01:40:20.149
there is a place

01:40:20.159 --> 01:40:28.310
for those who are lonely.

01:40:28.320 --> 01:40:31.990
Sing it again. I can hear your voice.

01:40:32.000 --> 01:40:34.950
I'm alone.

01:40:34.960 --> 01:40:38.229
I can hear

01:40:38.239 --> 01:40:42.790
the mountain of the Lord. I can

01:40:42.800 --> 01:40:45.910
touch your face.

01:40:45.920 --> 01:40:49.189
There is a place

01:40:49.199 --> 01:40:52.550
for those who are

01:40:52.560 --> 01:40:57.590
in the mountain of the Lord.

01:40:57.600 --> 01:41:00.310
I can feel the

01:41:00.320 --> 01:41:04.070
mountain

01:41:07.679 --> 01:41:11.030
of

01:41:11.040 --> 01:41:15.109
your blessing.

01:41:15.119 --> 01:41:18.790
There is a place.

01:41:22.239 --> 01:41:29.590
I said there is a place

01:41:29.600 --> 01:41:45.430
in the

01:41:45.430 --> 01:41:45.440
cleft

01:41:45.440 --> 01:41:49.830
of the Lord.

01:41:49.840 --> 01:41:53.830
I just love his ministry

01:41:53.840 --> 01:41:56.709
of all the people that... whenever he

01:41:56.719 --> 01:41:58.470
knew how to hit those... when he

01:41:58.480 --> 01:41:59.830
started to worship and you could feel

01:41:59.840 --> 01:42:01.830
the vein

01:42:01.840 --> 01:42:03.350
every single time I listen to him, I

01:42:03.360 --> 01:42:11.910
just go, 'My

01:42:11.910 --> 01:42:11.920
goodness.'I

01:42:11.920 --> 01:42:14.149
try to, you know, whenever there's

01:42:14.159 --> 01:42:16.870
nights like this, to lead by example,

01:42:16.870 --> 01:42:16.880
an

01:42:16.880 --> 01:42:19.030
example

01:42:19.040 --> 01:42:22.390
of teaching you how. It's just awkward

01:42:22.400 --> 01:42:25.590
because if it was private, I

01:42:25.600 --> 01:42:27.990
know it's a lot easier for me to do that

01:42:28.000 --> 01:42:29.990
whenever I know the certain things that

01:42:30.000 --> 01:42:34.070
I would sing that are private to me. But

01:42:34.080 --> 01:42:36.310
bringing it to you because there's so

01:42:36.320 --> 01:42:38.629
many of you that think it's just

01:42:38.639 --> 01:42:41.830
something you just... the

01:42:41.840 --> 01:42:43.109
critics don't get it because they're

01:42:43.119 --> 01:42:46.229
never going to walk in it anyway. 99% of

01:42:46.239 --> 01:42:49.990
them will never walk in that place.

01:42:50.000 --> 01:42:51.270
But there are some of you that are so

01:42:51.280 --> 01:42:54.310
desperate that you want it so bad

01:42:54.320 --> 01:42:56.070
that you really truly want a

01:42:56.080 --> 01:42:58.310
relationship with the Lord. Not what

01:42:58.320 --> 01:43:01.270
Brandon has, but just your own thing.

01:43:01.280 --> 01:43:03.109
And I'm trying to teach you by example, by

01:43:03.119 --> 01:43:06.470
what I do by finding the

01:43:06.480 --> 01:43:09.669
books, finding things, and you grasp on

01:43:09.679 --> 01:43:12.229
to it, and this

01:43:12.239 --> 01:43:13.830
is how you pull yourself out of even

01:43:13.840 --> 01:43:15.590
this dry season. I haven't been dry all

01:43:15.600 --> 01:43:17.910
day. It just was weird. This is weird

01:43:17.920 --> 01:43:21.669
what happened.

01:43:21.679 --> 01:43:24.709
But getting in that place of that

01:43:24.719 --> 01:43:26.950
refreshing of where you cultivate

01:43:26.960 --> 01:43:28.790
his presence,

01:43:28.800 --> 01:43:30.470
out of your belly shall flow

01:43:30.480 --> 01:43:33.030
rivers of living waters and

01:43:33.040 --> 01:43:34.709
you

01:43:34.719 --> 01:43:36.790
bring yourself up by your bootstraps and

01:43:36.800 --> 01:43:38.790
not be moved by what you see or what

01:43:38.800 --> 01:43:41.990
you feel,

01:43:42.000 --> 01:43:45.350
by just being authentic and real,

01:43:45.360 --> 01:43:49.830
Father. And most people will quit

01:43:49.840 --> 01:43:51.669
and they don't let it go because they

01:43:51.679 --> 01:43:54.229
have seasons of dryness and

01:43:54.239 --> 01:43:56.950
they

01:43:56.960 --> 01:43:58.870
think, 'Well, if this is what it

01:43:58.880 --> 01:44:00.709
is, I get tired.'You're always looking

01:44:00.719 --> 01:44:02.629
at your watch:

01:44:02.639 --> 01:44:04.950
'How long have I been in prayer today?

01:44:04.960 --> 01:44:08.149
How long have I been doing this?

01:44:08.159 --> 01:44:11.189
Is he really

01:44:11.189 --> 01:44:11.199
there?'And

01:44:11.199 --> 01:44:12.950
regardless of what I feel right now,

01:44:12.960 --> 01:44:16.790
even with all you

01:44:16.800 --> 01:44:21.590
sitting here in my living room,

01:44:21.600 --> 01:44:23.750
I'm not moved by what I see or what I

01:44:23.760 --> 01:44:26.629
feel. That's where you pull yourself out

01:44:26.639 --> 01:44:30.629
of that. Faith is not a feeling.

01:44:30.639 --> 01:44:33.669
Faith is an act.

01:44:33.679 --> 01:44:35.510
Faith doesn't have to be the glory and

01:44:35.520 --> 01:44:37.109
you seeing things and the holy angel

01:44:37.119 --> 01:44:39.669
choir and all that you feel. Faith is an

01:44:39.679 --> 01:44:43.430
act. I refuse to be moved by my flesh. I

01:44:43.440 --> 01:44:45.350
move by what the spirit is. And he

01:44:45.360 --> 01:44:47.990
said he inhabits the praises of his

01:44:48.000 --> 01:44:52.790
people. And he's

01:44:52.800 --> 01:44:54.709
always there. He's never left me.

01:44:54.709 --> 01:44:54.719
He's

01:44:54.719 --> 01:44:56.709
never forsaken me. Lo, unto the end of

01:44:56.719 --> 01:44:58.149
the earth, he said he'd be with us

01:44:58.159 --> 01:45:00.470
always. And either you have a mindset of

01:45:00.480 --> 01:45:05.109
that and you realize it, or you don't.

01:45:05.119 --> 01:45:08.629
It's not a feeling.

01:45:08.639 --> 01:45:10.550
Prayer comes out of...

01:45:10.560 --> 01:45:13.189
sometimes I hear a lady say to me,

01:45:13.199 --> 01:45:15.510
'Brandon, I don't see anything when

01:45:15.520 --> 01:45:19.030
I pray; I just

01:45:19.030 --> 01:45:19.040
pray.'Who

01:45:19.040 --> 01:45:21.910
said you were ever going to?

01:45:21.920 --> 01:45:23.590
Blessed are those that have not seen, yet

01:45:23.600 --> 01:45:26.870
still believe.

01:45:26.880 --> 01:45:31.910
And so you just keep pushing on.

01:45:31.920 --> 01:45:33.350
Does that make sense what I'm saying,

01:45:33.360 --> 01:45:35.189
son?

01:45:35.199 --> 01:45:36.950
Because I try to make it where it's not

01:45:36.960 --> 01:45:38.550
so—where

01:45:38.560 --> 01:45:40.310
there's so many people

01:45:40.320 --> 01:45:44.709
always trying to

01:45:44.709 --> 01:45:44.719
parrot

01:45:44.719 --> 01:45:46.950
it,

01:45:46.960 --> 01:45:49.030
where you find

01:45:49.040 --> 01:45:51.750
your own. But even when you see—this

01:45:51.750 --> 01:45:51.760
is a

01:45:51.760 --> 01:45:54.310
struggle versus just authentic, like

01:45:54.320 --> 01:45:56.229
it was last time when I felt like the

01:45:56.239 --> 01:45:58.149
glory of the Lord showed up in the whole

01:45:58.159 --> 01:46:00.229
house and I could feel it was

01:46:00.239 --> 01:46:02.070
tangible.

01:46:02.080 --> 01:46:05.750
You know, does that make sense? Yes.

01:46:05.760 --> 01:46:07.910
I try to make sense instead,

01:46:07.920 --> 01:46:09.350
because when I'm talking and leading

01:46:09.360 --> 01:46:12.149
these people,

01:46:12.159 --> 01:46:15.430
how you push through it. So then you go

01:46:15.440 --> 01:46:18.070
back in; I start worshiping and you sit

01:46:18.080 --> 01:46:19.990
there, and that's why I say sometimes I

01:46:20.000 --> 01:46:24.870
sit there for five hours and nothing.

01:46:24.880 --> 01:46:26.870
You feel like you've been there for five hours, and

01:46:26.880 --> 01:46:28.709
I'll be

01:46:28.719 --> 01:46:30.950
sitting at my dryer. Usually I sit by my

01:46:30.960 --> 01:46:33.030
dryer because I'm doing laundry,

01:46:33.040 --> 01:46:35.590
helping Diana with laundry, and I sit

01:46:35.600 --> 01:46:38.790
there for an hour, five hours, nothing.

01:46:38.800 --> 01:46:42.390
It's like—and then finally you'll hit it

01:46:42.400 --> 01:46:44.070
and you'll push over and you'll start to

01:46:44.080 --> 01:46:45.750
see.

01:46:45.760 --> 01:46:49.590
And sometimes it'll be all day long,

01:46:49.600 --> 01:46:52.310
nothing. And you'll go, 'What?'And I'm

01:46:52.320 --> 01:46:54.709
just praying. You just, 'Father, I just

01:46:54.719 --> 01:46:56.790
worship you.'And you're going, 'Are you

01:46:56.800 --> 01:46:58.310
ever going to show up?'I'm looking for

01:46:58.320 --> 01:47:01.590
that tug on the tugboat.

01:47:01.600 --> 01:47:05.189
Help push me out of this. Help me. Let's

01:47:05.199 --> 01:47:07.350
do this together.

01:47:07.360 --> 01:47:09.270
Sometimes it's just instantaneously you

01:47:09.280 --> 01:47:11.590
just step right over in it. But I

01:47:11.590 --> 01:47:11.600
have

01:47:11.600 --> 01:47:14.950
always learned:

01:47:14.960 --> 01:47:17.350
it's always different.

01:47:17.360 --> 01:47:19.109
And sometimes the more you cultivate,

01:47:19.119 --> 01:47:21.109
it's easier. But even when I asked

01:47:21.119 --> 01:47:23.430
him today—I knew

01:47:23.440 --> 01:47:25.270
what he was saying, but I didn't realize

01:47:25.280 --> 01:47:26.550
it was going to be like this to this

01:47:26.560 --> 01:47:28.390
degree. But when I was in there and I

01:47:28.400 --> 01:47:30.550
told him, he goes, 'I want you

01:47:30.560 --> 01:47:32.709
to show them by example, humble

01:47:32.719 --> 01:47:35.109
yourself.

01:47:35.119 --> 01:47:39.750
Show them it's not always like

01:47:39.750 --> 01:47:39.760
that.'I

01:47:39.760 --> 01:47:43.590
said, 'Okay,

01:47:43.600 --> 01:47:46.470
I get

01:47:46.470 --> 01:47:46.480
it.'So

01:47:46.480 --> 01:47:49.430
hopefully it helps you. I don't know

01:47:49.440 --> 01:47:51.430
if it does or not, but if it doesn't,

01:47:51.440 --> 01:47:53.270
then you say, 'Well, Brandon, this was a

01:47:53.280 --> 01:47:54.790
waste of time.'You just click out and

01:47:54.800 --> 01:47:57.510
go on. But at least I

01:47:57.520 --> 01:48:00.310
can say I tried

01:48:00.320 --> 01:48:02.390
to teach you all as much as I can, and

01:48:02.400 --> 01:48:03.750
hopefully you're getting something out

01:48:03.760 --> 01:48:06.149
of it. Find—that's

01:48:06.149 --> 01:48:06.159
when you

01:48:06.159 --> 01:48:08.390
find the

01:48:08.400 --> 01:48:09.990
scriptures

01:48:09.990 --> 01:48:10.000
that

01:48:10.000 --> 01:48:11.910
pertain to what you're

01:48:11.920 --> 01:48:13.910
believing for. You go through it. And

01:48:13.920 --> 01:48:17.510
lately,

01:48:17.520 --> 01:48:20.229
I've been reading

01:48:20.239 --> 01:48:24.709
Jeremiah over and over and over,

01:48:24.719 --> 01:48:27.830
and how he went through things where

01:48:27.840 --> 01:48:30.870
it seemed like he was all alone, where it

01:48:30.880 --> 01:48:33.030
seemed like he was talking

01:48:33.040 --> 01:48:34.550
to people and they wanted to kill him

01:48:34.560 --> 01:48:36.790
for it. They didn't like what he was

01:48:36.800 --> 01:48:39.109
saying. And the other false prophets

01:48:39.119 --> 01:48:40.790
were telling everybody everything was

01:48:40.800 --> 01:48:42.790
going to be great. And here he was

01:48:42.800 --> 01:48:46.470
telling everybody that it's going to

01:48:46.480 --> 01:48:49.109
be judgment and all these other

01:48:49.119 --> 01:48:50.790
things coming. And they're all telling,

01:48:50.800 --> 01:48:52.390
'Oh, he's a false

01:48:52.390 --> 01:48:52.400
prophet.'And

01:48:52.400 --> 01:48:54.390
he was the only one—he was

01:48:54.400 --> 01:48:55.910
the voice crying in the

01:48:55.910 --> 01:48:55.920
wilderness—the

01:48:55.920 --> 01:48:57.270
only one saying what God told him to

01:48:57.280 --> 01:48:59.270
really say. And they were ready to kill

01:48:59.280 --> 01:49:03.109
him for it. The kings hated him.

01:49:03.119 --> 01:49:06.149
And so, going over... the Lord

01:49:06.159 --> 01:49:08.310
said, 'Read it again. Read it again. Go

01:49:08.320 --> 01:49:10.390
over things.'Faith cometh by hearing, and

01:49:10.400 --> 01:49:12.870
hearing by the word of God.

01:49:12.880 --> 01:49:16.070
And so I know reading Hebrews and

01:49:16.080 --> 01:49:17.669
going over that,

01:49:17.679 --> 01:49:20.310
stirring yourself up.

01:49:20.320 --> 01:49:21.990
But not only that, but leading your

01:49:22.000 --> 01:49:23.669
